Assuming you&#39;re working in a JavaScript environment, you can convert the outer object to an array and then access elements by index. Here&#39;s an example:

    const jsonData = {
       &quot;http://url.com/&quot;: {
          &quot;id&quot;: &quot;http://url.com//&quot;
       },
       &quot;http://url2.co/&quot;: {
